        <div class="comment-content">
            <blockquote>...if you are multitasking, every estimate you have is wrong. Guaranteed.</blockquote>

<p>Gold!  Pure gold!  I cannot understand why people just don't believe this to be the case, but I see it happen time and time again.</p>

<p>Dave Rooney<br />
